title: Last Week in Slovakia: Tens of thousands marched in tribute for the murdered couple
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
March 7, 2018
Pressure mounts on the government to resign. 
Tens of thousands marched at the #AllForJan marches around Slovakia and abroad. 
Pravda daily has a new owner, who also owns an "alternative news" website. 

This programme is part of The Slovak Spectator subscription and our readers are receiving it every Thursday morning as part of their subscription.
